Chaussette To improve my skills in mastering the symbolic execution framework, I tried to solve this challenge with as many means as possible. I skipped the first reversing part which is not the interest here. Introduction about the challenge The goal of the challenge is to solve a lot of “puzzle”, which consist of a entry of arguments (RDI and RSI (System V ABI x86_64 calling convention)). The goal is to find input when RAX==0 at the end of the shellcode.
